{"word":"G5001 - τάγμα - tágma - tag'-mah - Order","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τάγμα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">tágma</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">tag'-mah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Order</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"வரிசை - பால்வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. that which has been arranged, thing placed in order"},{"paragraph":"2. a body of soldiers, a corps"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5021 - τάσσω - tássō - tas'-so/5021\">G5021</a>; something orderly in <i>arrangement</i> (a <i>troop</i>), that is, (figuratively) a <i>series</i> or <i>succession:</i> - order.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1296/1296\">G1296</a>, <a href=\"#/G1297/1297\">G1297</a>, <a href=\"#/G1299/1299\">G1299</a>, <a href=\"#/G2004/2004\">G2004</a>, <a href=\"#/G392/392\">G392</a>, <a href=\"#/G4367/4367\">G4367</a>, <a href=\"#/G5001/5001\">G5001</a>, <a href=\"#/G5021/5021\">G5021</a>, <a href=\"#/G506/506\">G506</a>, <a href=\"#/G5292/5292\">G5292</a>, <a href=\"#/G5293/5293\">G5293</a>, <a href=\"#/G657/657\">G657</a>, <a href=\"#/G812/812\">G812</a>, <a href=\"#/G813/813\">G813</a>, <a href=\"#/G814/814\">G814</a>"}]}